    "descSichuan": "Famous for its bold flavors, pungency, and spiciness from garlic and chili peppers.",
    "regionCantonese": "Cantonese Cuisine",
    "descCantonese": "Known for fresh ingredients and minimal spices. Dim Sum is a highlight.",
    "regionJiangsu": "Jiangsu Cuisine",
