    "descShenzhen": "China's original Special Economic Zone - a futuristic megacity built in just 40 years.",
    "descSilk": "5,000 years of the world's finest fabric \u2014 from imperial robes to the Silk Road",
    "descTea": "Discover the art of \u8336\u9053 \u2014 Gongfu tea, fine teaware, and the philosophy of harmony in Chinese tea culture.",
    "heroTitlePaper": "Chinese Paper Cutting",
    "metaDescTransport": "Explore China's modern transportation network \u2014 from high-speed rail and metro systems to aviation and highways. Plan your journey across China with ease.",
    "metaDescXiaolongbao": "Xiaolongbao \u2014 delicate soup dumplings filled with pork and broth, a signature dish from Shanghai.",
